{
  "page": "Feature quote/34",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“<a href=\"/index.php/Merrett_Frey\" title=\"Merrett Frey\">Father</a> had only gone out to ransom <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Frey\" title=\"Petyr Frey\">Petyr Pimple</a>. He brought them the gold they asked for, but <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_Without_Banners\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brotherhood Without Banners\">they</a> hung him anyway.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Amerei_Frey\" title=\"Amerei Frey\">Amerei “Gatehouse Ami” Frey</a><br />“Hanged, Ami. Your father was not a tapestry.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Mariya_Darry\" title=\"Mariya Darry\">Mariya Darry</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_30\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 30\">Chapter 30</a>, Jaime IV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404012108\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.021 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 82/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 303/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 524/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   15.212      1 -total\n100.00%   15.212      1 Template:Ref\n 30.20%    4.594      1 Template:Ref